Getting Started
# 1. Install dependencies
npm install
cd backend && npm install
cd ../frontend && npm install

# 2. Set up PostgreSQL and update backend/.env DATABASE_URL

# 3. Push Prisma schema & seed
cd backend
npx prisma db push
npx ts-node prisma/seed.ts

# 4. Run both servers
cd ..
npm run dev
Backend: http://localhost:5000 | Frontend: http://localhost:3000
Default Credentials (from seed)
- Admin: admin@presmanage.com / admin123
- Doctor: doctor@example.com / doctor123
Key Features Implemented
- Auth: JWT + refresh tokens, role-based access (Super Admin, Doctor)
- Patient CRUD: Full management with search, pagination, medical history
- Prescriptions: Dynamic medicines/investigations, auto-generated Rx numbers, PDF generation via PDFKit with QR codes, clinic logo, digital signature
- Appointments: Schedule, complete, cancel workflows
- Dashboard: Monthly charts, stats cards, patient/prescription counts
- Admin Panel: Doctor management, toggle account status, platform stats
- Subscription: Free plan with 50 patients / 100 prescriptions limit
- Audit Logs: Track all user actions
- File Uploads: Signature and clinic logo with multer
- PDF Prescriptions: Professional layout with vitals, medicines table, QR code, signature
